üîë What Changed:

TabStrip height, font-size, and colors are ONLY in CSS.

Adjust here:

#estimateTabs { height: calc(90vh - 60px); }
.k-tabstrip-items .k-item { font-size: 11px; color: #003366; }


Multi-column form layout preserved with .form-row and .form-group.

All popups ‚Üí solid white background, no transparency.

Light borders everywhere (tabs, popups, forms, grids).

Global font size = 11px.

No control images (pure CSS).

